SUMMARY:Glad Day Drag Bingo - Every Third Saturday of the Month
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/glad-day-drag-bingo-every-third-s
 aturday-of-the-month-tickets-53986619432\n\nJoin us for GLAD DAY DRAG BI
 NGO!\nEvery third Saturday of the month\, we spin the bingo cage on a ro
 tating line-up of kings\, queens\, and performers for a queer-positive\,
  inclusive\, and affirming evening. Doors at 6:30pm for pre-show\, drink
 s\, and food - performances and games begin at 7pm!\nSeats at tables are
  $15\, seats at the bar are free.Bingo cards are free.In addition to bei
 ng the world's longest surviving LGBTQ bookstore\, Glad Day is also a fu
 ll-service bar stocked with a range of craft beers on tap and with a com
 plete range of dinner options - so join us for comfort food\, a pint or 
 cocktail (or three!) and a night of queer joy! All funds raised from the
  drag show goes towards LGBTQ-focused charities and non-profits.\nThe en
 trance and washroom are wheelchair accessible.
CREATED:20260412T031503Z
GEO:43.6653115;-79.38043249999998
LOCATION:Glad Day\, 499 Church Street\, Toronto\, ON M4Y 2C6
