SUMMARY:Glad Day Drag Bingo
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/glad-day-drag-bingo-tickets-53451
 932168\n\nJoin us Saturday\, December 15th for GLAD DAY DRAG BINGO!\nEve
 ry third Saturday of the month\, we spin the bingo cage on a rotating li
 ne-up of kings\, queens\, and performers for a queer-positive\, inclusiv
 e\, and affirming evening\, with all proceeds from bingo card sales goin
 g to charity! Join us 6:30pm for pre-show\, drinks\, and food - performa
 nces and games begin at 7pm!\nThis month\, performers Juice Boxx and Dev
 on Cream join our bingo caller Nyree for a night of music\, food\, perfo
 rmances\, prizes and fun!\nIn addition to being the world's longest surv
 iving LGBTQ bookstore\, Glad Day is also a full-service bar stocked with
  a range of craft beers on tap and with a complete range of dinner optio
 ns - so join us for comfort food\, a pint or cocktail (or three!) and a 
 night of queer joy!
