DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/samuel-r-delany-sex-radical-afro-
 futurist-and-grandmaster-of-science-fiction-tickets-28934477802\n\nSAMUE
 L R. DELANY Sex Radical\, Afro-Futurist and Grandmaster of Science Ficti
 on\nIn his first Toronto appearance in over 20 years\, Samuel R. Delany 
 talks writing\, sex\, race\, afro-futurism and science fiction. Using th
 e talk show style interview\, our moderator Njeri Damali Campbell will a
 sk 'Chip' Delany a range of questions\, from the personal to the politic
 al\, from the casual to the creative. In the second half\, the audience 
 gets to ask Chip thier own questions at this once-in-a-lifetime opportun
 ity with a legend.\nThis event is part of the Naked Heart Festival. The 
 Naked Heart Festival is the world's largest LGBTQ literary festival and 
 is organized by Glad Day Lit.\nThe space and the washrooms are wheelchai
 r accessible.ASL will be provided at this event.\n$18 in advance$20 at t
 he doorThis event is FREE if you have a Naked Heart Festival pass ($39\,
  or $19 for youth and seniors\nSpace is limited so Festival Pass holders
  and advance ticket holders will get priority seating.\nFor more informa
 tion\, contact: michael@gladday.ca
